                  </persName> was <hi rend="italic">again</hi> indicted<rs id="t18660507-465-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18660507-465-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18660507-465-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp> for stealing 3 spoons and 9 forks of <persName id="t18660507-name-148" type="victimName">
